  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They don't go together, but I had them altogether and got a certificate, which-- which enabled me to practice psychotherapy in Germany, which I, of course, never did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I for now was secure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had some private practice, mainly in marriage counseling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I did very much marriage counseling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did very little depth therapy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I've [INAUDIBLE] [? to do ?] this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had seen so much of life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, myself, [INAUDIBLE] a very happy marriage, [? so ?] I did mainly marriage counseling.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was also teaching at George Washington University.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started as an associate lecturer and was-- within a year, was full-time professorial status of the-- of the chief of the [? unit. ?] And I was consultant [? over ?] to- to Walter Reed Army Hospital and consultant to the counseling center of the University of Maryland there on a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wrote which-- which I had on my mind all the time to write and which had-- which had two more editions under the name of-- of, actually, first a hardcover edition and then a softcover edition of-- of the same subject as the-- the same books.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's only very little changes inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And had an additional chapter, which deals mainly with Lore and me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I wrote Did you read it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- this was very much on my mind, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wrote many articles, psychological professional articles-- I think 12 or 14-- which were transferred to other languages.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of research went into your writing?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've-- I have your books.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I've noted--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well,--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my older son, he's employed as a research psychologist by the Library of Congress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he's-- he provided me with many data.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
